`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
`tickHunger` and `tickHeartsFrom*` are designed as pure value functions — no entity mutation. This mirrors the `regenStamina` (returns new value) pattern from `stamina.ts`, keeping all survival logic testable with plain numbers. The stamina drain adds a difficulty multiplier that `drainStamina` in `stamina.ts` lacks, making it the canonical place for survival-mode action costs.
